<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en" lang="en">
	<head>
		<%= stylesheet_link_tag @plugin_css, 'common' %>
		<%= yield :stylesheets %>
		<%#= ajaxful_rating_style %>
		<%= stylesheet_link_tag @theme_css %>
		
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<title><%= yield :title %></title>

		<%= site_meta_tags %>
		<%= javascript_include_tag 'swfobject_modified' if @page && @page.id == 1 %>
		<%= javascript_include_tag 'ckeditor/ckeditor.js' if current_user && current_user.has_role?('admin') && ['new', 'edit'].include?(action_name) %>
		<%= javascript_include_tag 'jquery.all' %>
		<%= yield :scripts %>
		<%= javascript_include_tag @plugins %>
	  	<%= javascript_include_tag 'greymatter', 'application' %>
		<%#= javascript_include_tag 'queryLoader' if @page %>
	  	<%= @widgets_js.map { |js| javascript_include_tag js } %>
    
		<link rel="shortcut icon" href="/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon" />
		
		<!--[if IE]>
			<script src="http://html5shiv.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js"></script>
		<![endif]-->
		
		<!--[if lte IE 7]>
			<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="stylesheets/ie.css" />
		<![endif]-->
	</head>
	<body id="<%= controller_name %>_controller" class="<%= action_name %>_action <%= page_name + (@page.nil? || @page.new_record? ? ' non_page' : '') %><%= current_user ? ' authenticated' : '' %><%= current_user && current_user.has_role?('admin') ? ' admin' : '' %>">
	
	<div id="topbar">
		<%= render :partial => 'menus/topnav' %>
	</div> <!-- /#wrapper -->
	
	<div id="body" class="wrapper">
		<div id="logo">
			<a href="/"><img src="/images/ui/storagelocator/us-self-storage-locator-logo.png" alt="US Self Storage Locator" /></a>
			<img src="/images/ui/storagelocator/us-self-storage-locator-heading.png" alt="US Self Storage Locator" />
			<h1>Locate, Select and Reserve Self Storage Anywhere, Anytime.</h1>
		</div>
		
		<% form_tag '/self-storage', :id => 'front_search' do %>
			<p class="hide">Enter a zip code, city, or street address to begin searching.</p>
			<div id="search_field">
				<%= text_field_tag :q, nil, :class => 'hintable', :title => 'Enter Zip Code, City, or Street Address' %>
				<%= submit_tag 'Locate', :class => 'grn_btn' %>
				<p id="ab"><a href="#" class="openDiv" rel="advanced_opts">Advanced Options</a></p>
			</div>
			
			<div id="advanced_opts">
				<p id="ao_top">Choose your options for a refined Self Storage search:</p>
					<div class="left">
						<div>
							<%= label_tag 'Type:' %>
							<%= select_tag 'storage_type', ['<option>Self Storage</option><option>Mobile Storage</option>'] %>
						</div>
						
						<div id="size_picker">
							<img src="/images/ui/storagelocator/temp-size-img.jpg" alt="Size" />
						</div>
						
						<div>
							<%= label_tag 'Unit Size:' %>
							<%= select_tag 'storage_size', ['<option>5 x 7</option><option>10 x 10</option>'] %>
						</div>
					</div>
					
					<div class="right">
						<div class="top">
							<div id="slide_wrap">
								<%= label_tag 'Within' %>
								<div class="slider"></div>
								<%= label_tag 'miles.' %>
							</div>
							
							<div id="loc_btn">
								<%= submit_tag 'Locate', :class => 'grn_btn' %>
							</div>
						</div>
						
						<div class="bottom">
							<p><%= label_tag 'Features:' %></p>
							
							<div id="features">
								<% 1.upto(20) do |i| %>
									<div class="feature_check">
										<%= check_box_tag 'storage_features', "feature_#{i}" %>
										<%= label_tag "Feature #{i}" %>
									</div>
								<% end %>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		<% end %>
		
		<%= yield %>

	</div> <!-- /#body -->
		
	<div id="footer">
		<div id="footer_top">
			<div class="divide">
				<p class="wrapper">Need to find Self Storage? It's Easy!</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<div id="footer_mid">
			<div id="steps">
				<div id="step1" class="step">
					<h3>Locate</h3>
					<p>
						Locate a self storage facility that suits your needs! Narrow your results by city, zip code, or street address. You can even choose to search by unit size, distance from your home, and facility amenities.
					</p>
				</div>
				
				<div id="step2" class="step">
					<h3>Select</h3>
					<p>
						Select a self storage facility that has exactly what you need using our feature enhanced, easy-to-use locator. You can sort locations by distance and features so you can find your perfect self-storage solution with ease.
					</p>
				</div>
				
				<div id="step3" class="step last">
					<h3>Reserve</h3>
					<p>
						Reserve your final choice with one final easy step. You’ll reserve the self storage unit you chose and be able to take advantage of our exclusive discount offers. Once your confirmation e-mail is sent, you’re good to go! 
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div id="more_info">
				<h4>USSelfStorageLocator.com Helps<br> You Find a Self Storage Unit Anywhere Anytime!</h4>
				
				<div class="inner">
					<p>
						<img class="right" src="/files/content/more-info-pic.png" alt="Self Storage Reservations" />
					</p>
					<p>
						Let’s face it, we accumulate a lot of stuff. Growing families, new purchases, or relocations all create the need for more space in our lives. When your possessions outgrow your living space, or you need to move to another location, consider self storage!
					</p>
						
					<h5>Options, Options, &amp; More Options</h4>
					<p>
						There are many types of self-storage facilities to choose from – they range from simple home goods storage to specialized facilities for vehicle owners, boat captains, and businesses. You can choose between self storage facilities and mobile storage, climate controlled units, various bay sizes, indoor and outdoor facilities, minimal and high security – the list goes on! With all of these options, you may find yourself needing some serious storage help.
					</p>
						
					<h5>We Make Deciding Easy</h4>
					<p>
						Whether you’re looking for storage help, moving solutions, or you’re a storage facility looking to <a href="http://storagelocator.heroku.com/add-your-facility"><strong>advertise your services</strong></a>, <a href="http://storagelocator.heroku.com"><strong>USSelfStorageLocator.com</strong></a> can help!
					</p>
						
					<p>
						<a href="http://storagelocator.heroku.com"><strong>USSelfStorageLocator.com</strong></a> makes it easy for you to research all of your self storage needs and questions. Here, you can find and compare <a href="http://storagelocator.heroku.com/storage-locator"><strong>self storage facilities</strong></a> by location, amenities, and storage type, learn what packing essentials (link to packing and supplies) you will need to protect important items, and browse our many tips!
					</p>
						
					<p>
						If you have a specific question and haven’t found the answer here, please <a href="http://storagelocator.heroku.com"><strong>contact us!</strong></a>
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div id="handle"></div>
			<a href="#more_info" rel="more_info" id="red_tab">Click to open</a>
			
		</div>
		
		<div id="footer_btm">
			<div class="strip"></div>
			
			<div class="wrapper">
				<div class="ad"></div>
				<div class="ad"></div>
				<div class="ad"></div>
				<div class="ad"></div>
				<div class="ad"></div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	
	</body>
</html>




